    "dialogue": [
        {
            "text": "I am Merric, a mage from Altea. What I learned of wind magic in Khadein is at your disposal.",
            "context": "joined"
        },
        {
            "text": "May I ask about your summoning magic? You tie the skies together? Is that wind magic like my own?",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I studied in Khadein, the City of Magic. It was a remarkable place, with desert sand to the horizons...",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "Thank you for what you do. Your guidance keeps everyone motivated and safe.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I've known Prince Marth and his sister Princess Elice for many years. They are truly good people.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I've always been physically weak. But I wanted to protect...people precious to me, so I studied magic.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "Let's see now... You must be <Player Name>, right? I'm Merric—here with a hello from <Friend Name>!",
            "context": "friend"
        },
        {
            "text": "It seems the Excalibur tome has guided me well.",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "My body feels so light! I can move like the wind itself!",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "It seems I haven't trained enough. I will begin again with the basics.",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "I will use this new power to protect those precious to me.",
            "context": "growth"
        },
        {
            "text": "It's been some time since we began to fight side by side, yet you still find ways to surprise me. I don't mean that in a bad way! You're just...a very mysterious person. You're not like anyone I've met. The things you come up with...the rest of us have never dreamed of. You are like a wind that blows through each of our lives and changes our fates. So please know that I believe in you and your abilities. I will work with you as long as you'll have me.",
            "context": "maxed"
        }
    ],
